ZH: 我的胆子很小，不敢尝试任何刺激的活动。
EN: My courage is small and I dare not try any exciting activities.

ZH: 这个困难的挑战需要一颗强大的胆子。
EN: This challenging task requires a strong courage.

ZH: 他只有在很害怕的时候才会暴露出他的胆小。
EN: He only shows his cowardice when he is very scared.

ZH: 她的大胆举动让所有人感到惊讶。
EN: Her bold move surprised everyone.

ZH: 这个黑暗的地方让他的胆战心惊。
EN: The dark place made his heart skip a beat.

ZH: 他的胆囊需要进行手术治疗。
EN: His gallbladder needs to be treated with surgery.

ZH: 胆囊炎会给人造成极大的疼痛。
EN: Gallbladder inflammation can cause extreme pain.

ZH: 这个困难的挑战需要勇气和胆识。
EN: This challenging task requires courage and determination.

ZH: 他胆小如鼠，从不敢冒险。
EN: He is as timid as a mouse and never dares to take risks.

ZH: 前进的道路上需要乘风破浪的胆识。
EN: The road to progress requires the courage to face challenges.

ZH: 他的胆怯让他错失了很多机会。
EN: His timidity has caused him to miss out on many opportunities.

ZH: 在困难面前，我们需要坚强的胆识。
EN: In the face of difficulties, we need strong courage.

ZH: 她对未知的事物充满好奇，展现出了她的大胆。
EN: She is curious about the unknown and shows her boldness.

ZH: 他在危险面前展现了出色的勇气和胆识。
EN: He showed exceptional courage and determination in the face of danger.

ZH: 面对挑战，我们需要拥有足够的胆识。
EN: When facing challenges, we need to have enough courage.

ZH: 她的大胆和自信让她成为团队的领导。
EN: Her boldness and confidence make her a leader in the team.

ZH: 他在冰天雪地里表现出了惊人的胆量。
EN: He showed amazing courage in the icy wilderness.

ZH: 这次挑战需要我们齐心协力，勇气和胆识。
EN: This challenge requires us to work together, with courage and determination.

ZH: 她的决心和胆识使她成功地克服了困难。
EN: Her determination and courage enabled her to successfully overcome difficulties.

ZH: 他的胆囊手术很成功，现在已经康复了。
EN: His gallbladder surgery was successful and he has now recovered.
